  <entry>
    <title>「MMD 靜畫」賞花</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/03/13/MMDPic-20220313/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/03/13/MMDPic-20220313/</id>
    <published>2022-03-13T04:34:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-13T04:44:21.852Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//Tengu_20220313.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>春天也算是到了……吧？</p><p>最近突然就變熱了，明明還在三月，之後似乎還會降溫。</p><p>不知道本地的花有沒有開，果然還是希望能去看看。</p><p>能像三隻天狗一樣有朋友陪着去賞花就好了。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">OPTLETデジタル一眼レフカメラセット_v0.8 by mato.sus304</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　姫海棠はたて 改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">えと式 犬走椛 ver1.10</span><br><span class="line">Nukasa 草原</span><br><span class="line">31040 MMD用【桜の木(太）】</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">ikBokeh_v020a by ikeno</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">桜吹雪エフェクト ver2 by ビームマンP</span><br><span class="line">RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類 by 世界最弱のサーモントラウト</span><br><span class="line">Toon_RC by RedialC</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//Tengu_20220313.png&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;春天也算是到了……吧？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近突然就變熱了，明明還在三月，之後似乎還會降溫。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不知道本地的花有沒有開，果然還是希望能去看看。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;能像三隻天狗一樣有朋友陪着去賞花就好了。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
