  <entry>
    <title>「MMD 靜畫」喝茶時間</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/02/27/MMDPic-20220227/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/02/27/MMDPic-20220227/</id>
    <published>2022-02-26T16:02:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-02-26T16:21:11.850Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//AyaHatateMomiji_20220227.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>天狗們下班之後休息喝茶的時間，感覺會是很溫馨（也許）的場景。</p><p>感覺休息的時候和關係好的朋友在一起喝茶聊天會很棒。</p><p>雖然按照一設來椛椛和文的關係並不好，但是這是二次創作所以就沒問題（也許）。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">歌奈斗 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project 「射命丸文」モデルデータ</span><br><span class="line">歌奈斗 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project 「姫海棠はたて」モデルデータ</span><br><span class="line">すけ 東方Project　東方風神録　犬走　椛</span><br><span class="line">BK3 MikuMikuDance用モデル「和室テーブル」</span><br><span class="line">山田淀子 座布団</span><br><span class="line">徒然気まま 燭台</span><br><span class="line">徒然気まま 竹コップ</span><br><span class="line">キャベツ鉢 ポピュラーな果物セットver1.1</span><br><span class="line">NOB 紅葉と広間</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">ikBokeh_v020a by ikeno</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//AyaHatateMomiji_20220227.png&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;天狗們下班之後休息喝茶的時間，感覺會是很溫馨（也許）的場景。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;感覺休息的時候和關係好的朋友在一起喝茶聊天會很棒。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;雖然按照一設來椛椛和文的關係並不好，但是這是二次創作所以就沒問題（也許）。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
