  <entry>
    <title>「MMD 靜畫」春雪</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/02/19/MMDPic-20220219/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/2022/02/19/MMDPic-20220219/</id>
    <published>2022-02-19T14:27:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-02-19T14:47:05.112Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//AyaHatate_20220219.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><p>前幾日市內下了大雪，不知是因爲不久前就下過雨還是什麼，完全沒有積雪留下。</p><p>總之這張就是記者組在春日雪中散步拍照的圖。</p><p>輸出圖片的時候發現並沒有粒子效果出現，不知道是爲什麼。最後選了輸出視頻並截取其中一幀的方式得到圖片。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">OPTLETデジタル一眼レフカメラセット_v0.8 by mato.sus304</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　姫海棠はたて 改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">携帯型カメラ by フリック</span><br><span class="line">崖の山道 by  NuKasa</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">ikBokeh_v020a by ikeno</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">MikuMikuEffect用 吹雪エフェクト Ver.1.1 by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//AyaHatate_20220219.png&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;前幾日市內下了大雪，不知是因爲不久前就下過雨還是什麼，完全沒有積雪留下。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;總之這張就是記者組在春日雪中散步拍照的圖。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;輸出圖片的時候發現並沒有粒子效果出現，不知道是爲什麼。最後選了輸出視頻並截取其中一幀的方式得到圖片。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
